{{Orphan|date=August 2016}}

'''Louis Chapotot''' (17th century) was a French scientific instrument maker.

French maker of optical and mathematical instruments. Worked in [[Paris]], 1670-1686. Produced many types of instruments, including simple [[microscope]]s. His son, whose first name is not known, continued the business.

